ood.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2320e1b6214fc5230149364b4fc6c85fa21b0ff5","tid":780302,"uid":133920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T08:51:18.000Z","msg":"又冇話錯唔錯嘅<br />\n不過唔係最好嘅做法<br />\n如果你愛一個女仔<br />\n個女仔又同緊其他人一齊<br />\n個女仔開心咪暗地裡祝福人咪算<br />\n等到個女仔分手啦真係先再表白"},{"pid":"2317ed87fb869ed46230161e64dd41a4892f13ee","tid":780302,"uid":140798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"你有條女 你想唔想厹同你條女表白"},{"pid":"e00e33289744096844addbabdb4cf919c602b324","tid":780302,"uid":86403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:54:50.000Z","msg":"表左就係麻煩製造者.同人表完<br />\n你唔知個女仔點諗,又唔知個女仔又會唔會同佢男友講.<br />\n之後又唔知人地個男友點諗你.<br />\n<br />\n呢D同朋友表達你鍾意邊個好過."},{"pid":"8f3ab62122766a444f08c27c35e0433a1e97ff65","tid":780302,"uid":50400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B7u6bMBlCXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB7u6bMBlCXw&d=bzEgjJDypzABWqFO%2B20nl0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7fe186ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B7u6bMBlCXw</a><br />\n拍戲既話有老公都照表啦<br />\n大家夠成熟既話無問題"},{"pid":"00ae58853a3419ce2841a024f9420b74f59628ab","tid":780302,"uid":173939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:04:48.000Z","msg":"都係嫁，晒時間，但你講完一定會舒服d"},{"pid":"84855ee69d0689b0d02f2a6cd4303d9cb0c8354a","tid":780302,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:05:10.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都信幸福係自己爭取嘅<br />\n<br />\n佢有老婆仔女都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b27ff5db8a81626a6d81850273579486f62f709","tid":780302,"uid":138279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"唔好搞人地啦，放係心味算"},{"pid":"c28c2af75022feb9b9e10dc130ad394c504a983a","tid":780302,"uid":57255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2317ed87fb869ed46230161e64dd41a4892f13ee","tid"